CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 28, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "First Milestone - Ira Vann Harris, sone of Mr. and Mrs. Charles (Teenie) Harris, celebrated his first birthday last Sunday.  He's off to a good start."
TitMainTitle: Ira Vann Harris wearing overalls, seated on table with hand in birthday cake, on porch of Charles "Teenie" Harris's house, 7604 Mulford Street, Homewood
